  "title": "-NEW- Accounts Executive/Accountant",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>·       \nReview\nand approve AR invoices, AP invoices, and payment vouchers to ensure accuracy\nand completeness</p><p>·       \nReview\nand monitor related-party transactions in compliance with internal policies and\nregulatory requirements</p><p>·       \nReview\nmonthly account closing and prepare supporting schedules and reconciliations</p><p>·       \nPrepare\nconsolidated financial statements and management/statutory financial reports\nwithin reporting deadlines</p><p>·       \nHandle\nGST reporting, corporate tax filings, and deferred tax computations</p><p>·       \nEnsure\ncompliance with company policies, financial reporting standards, and statutory\nrequirements</p><p>·       \nPrepare\nand monitor cash flow reports to support financial planning and control</p><p>·       \nPerform\nother ad hoc duties and assignments as required</p><p>·       \nAdhoc\ntasks as assigned<br />\n<br />\n</p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>·       \nMinimum Degree\nin a related discipline</p><p>·       \nMinimum 3\nyears of relevant accounting duties </p><p>·       \nAble to\nstart immediately or within short notice</p><p>Interested candidates, kindly\nemail your detailed resumes in MS word format to <a href=\"mailto:josephkoh@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joseph.koh@ambition.com.sg</a>\n</p><p>Attention to Joseph Koh Wei Jie\n(R1873431)</p><p>Shortlisted candidates will be\nnotified</p><p><a href=\"http://www.ambition.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.ambition.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Registration Number: R1873431</p><p>Data provided is for recruitment\npurposes only</p><p>Business Registration Number:\n200611680D. License Number: 10C5117</p>",
